txt.en: Boss from the Vaults: Naruhel - Tier1

The Red-maid is lost -- or so it seems -- to the corruption wrought upon her land at the hands of Men. These men stand before her, ready to sacrifice themselves for the Red-maid, and they deserve this fate... and yet the nobility of your blood will be a greater reward for her. When these Men fall willingly before her, she will know the difference between those who help to strengthen, and those who seek to destroy.
You have returned to Garth Agarwen to defeat Naruhel, the Red-maid.
